10. h5 Nc6 11. hxg6 hxg6 12. Qg4 { The queen is headed for the h3-square. }
12... Ne7 13. O-O-O Re8 14. Qh3 Nf8 15. Nf3
{ Our position is a beautiful scheme. } *

