{ The sharpest and most popular try.   10...Rd8  11.O-O  Black has nothing better than  11...Bg4  ,  transposing to move 9... Bg4. Indeed, Bg4 is by far the most played move.  11...Be7  is dreadful due to d5 followed by Bxb6, when our center is just too strong. }
