{ We are breaking through. } 23... h6 24. exf6 Qd6
{ Black is still up an exchange, but Black will soon be forced to give it back. }
25. Bxh6 Rxf6 26. Bf4+ Rh6 27. Bxh6 gxh6 28. h3
{ Rd1 and Nb5 are decisive threats, while Black's king is practically naked. }
