16... Rxa7 { Black has to go for an endgame. } 17. d7+ Qxd7 18. cxd7+ Kxd7 19.
Ne5+ { It certainly doesn't hurt to throw in this check. } 19... Ke8 20. Nc6
Ra8 21. Be3 Nxa1 22. Na3
