5. Nf3 Bf5 6. Ne5
{ This reaction is extremely typical and a crucial idea to remember in the Scandinavian. Just like in the 3... Qe5+ line, we're aiming to harass the bishop with a subsequent g4-h4. }
6... e6 { Would be another error. } 7. g4
