10. O-O Bxc3 11. bxc3 Nd5 12. h5 { Black is now forced to play the ugly move }
12... f6 13. Nxg6 hxg6
{ Black's only hope is that there will be some counterplay down the h-file. }
14. c4 Ne7 15. Re1 { We just keep attacking the available targets. } 15... Qd6
16. Rb1 b6
{ White's advantage did not last long with the move  17.Qe2  in the game Baron Isanta, J - Garcia Ilundain, D Spain 1998. However, after the text move... }
17. Qf3 { The position will collapse after Ba3-d5. Black has no moves here. } *

