9. Be2 { Black now has a choice. } 9... Nc6
{ Was played in a 2600-GM encounter. } 10. h3
{ I think this simple move is the best approach, getting rid of the annoying bishop on g4.   10.Bh6  was played in Rublevksy, S - Ponkratov, P Sochi 2019, but I think Black has many ways to get a fine position. Ponkratov's choice of  10...Rfd8  was one of them. }
10... Bxf3 11. Bxf3 Rad8
