{ 15...axb5  16.Qb4  Rfe8  17.d6  is also good for White, when Rxb5 comes. }
16. Qe2
{ Black is on the verge of losing as our bishop pair and pawn on d5 is incredibly strong. }
16... Qb6 { Black has the cunning trap of Nxd5. } 17. Qe3
{ Forcing the trade of queens where we have a big edge. } *

