16. Be3 { Preventing Black from capturing the pawns on f2 and d4. } 16... Nxd4+
17. Bxd4 Bxd4 18. Bb5+ { A nice trick. } 18... axb5 19. Qxd4 Rd8 20. Qc5
{ White has everything under control, and will surely prevail. } *

