7. e5 Ne4 8. Nf3 { Let's defend the d4-pawn. } 8... Nxd2
{ Is Black's best choice, but it looks like a really bad French Defense. } 9.
Qxd2 e6 10. O-O
{ White will have all the fun. It should be noted that if Black ventures  10...Qxb2  we will be in the drivers seat with our extra development and space advantage.  11.Rab1  Qa3  12.Ng5  keeps the ball rolling. }
