14... Qf5 15. Bd3 Qxg5 16. Ne6+ Bxe6 17. Bxg5
{ Black is suddenly down material, but the game isn't lost yet. } 17... Bxd4
18. Qh4 { Attacking the bishop on d4 and pawn on e7 simultaneously. } 18...
Bxb2 19. Bxe7+ Kc8 20. Rb1 Bc3+ 21. Kf1
