Rad8 17. Bxg7
{ Our idea is to play Nef4, so we must rid ourselves of the bishop before we can do so. }
17... Kxg7 18. Nef4 Nxf4 19. Qxf4
{ Black's position is in dire straits due to our strong attack with h5 to come, but I still want to show a line which is slightly tricky. }
