10. c4 Nxc4 11. Qc2 { Black loses the c7-pawn in the end. } 11... Nb6 12. Qxc7
{ Black can only defend the knight with  12...h6  , when we get a winning endgame after  13.Qxb6  hxg5  14.Qb5+  , taking on  g5  after the queen trade. }
