9... Bd6
{ A very natural move is to protect the pawn on  e5  while completing the development. Note that  9...Bg7  is similar. }
10. dxe5
{ We should definitely not avoid opening up Black's camp, as his king is highly exposed at the moment. }
10... Nxe5 11. Nxe5+ Bxe5 12. O-O Ne7 13. Na3
