12. Be2 { I prefer keeping the bishop. } 12... Nf6 13. Ne5
{ It's time to jump to the center. } 13... Qc8 14. O-O
{ Keeping it simple.  14.f4  was played in Babiy, O - Stefanova, A Chess.com INT 2020, and certainly not too bad either. }
14... O-O 15. Rae1
{ White has a nice space advantage and can happily claim a clearly better game. }
