18... Nc6 { Is incredibly natural, but it's a decisive mistake } 19. Rf4
{ And we intrude in the f-file. } 19... h6
{ 19...Qe7  Can be refuted by  20.h6!  g6  21.Kg1+-  And we win as Black has no defense against Rf6 followed by Rf1 and Ng5. }
20. Rf6 { A fantastic winning move. Black can't stop Rxh6 as } 20... Kh8
{ Is mate immediately after } 21. Qg6 fxg6 22. Rxf8+ Kh7 23. hxg6#
{ Stunning! } *

